title: The 'breakfast club' and why Sam Darnold, Cooper Kupp aren't the first Seahawks at work

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: The 'breakfast club' and why Sam Darnold, Cooper Kupp aren't the first Seahawks at work
sources.description: A trio of unheralded Seattle defenders have been the first players into the team's practice facility for the past three years. This is their story.
